Batu Town is located at an average altitude of 871 m above sea level. Batu town surrounded by several mountains, among which are: Anjasmoro mountain (2277 m) Mt.Arjuno (3339 m) Many mountain Mt. Kawi (2651 m) Panderman mountain (2040 m) Welirang mountain (2156 m) As befits a region whose territory lush mountains, and surrounding Batu Panorama also has a beautiful nature and cool tube, of course this will attract other people to visit and enjoy the Batu mountainous region has its own charm.
